---------------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |EXCHANGE IN REMOTE                 |            |0       |979         |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT REMOTE              |            |0       |979         |
|2 |  └─TEMP TABLE TRANSFORMATION      |            |0       |979         |
|3 |    ├─TEMP TABLE INSERT            |TEMP1       |0       |979         |
|4 |    │ └─HASH GROUP BY              |            |0       |979         |
|5 |    │   └─HASH JOIN                |            |0       |979         |
|6 |    │     ├─TABLE FULL SCAN        |date_dim    |0       |39          |
|7 |    │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN        |store_sales |5000    |522         |
|8 |    └─TOP-N SORT                   |            |0       |0           |
|9 |      └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN           |            |0       |0           |
|10|        ├─HASH JOIN                |            |0       |0           |
|11|        │ ├─NESTED-LOOP JOIN       |            |0       |0           |
|12|        │ │ ├─SUBPLAN SCAN         |sb          |0       |0           |
|13|        │ │ │ └─HASH GROUP BY      |            |0       |0           |
|14|        │ │ │   └─TEMP TABLE ACCESS|VIEW2(TEMP1)|0       |0           |
|15|        │ │ └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET|store       |1       |16          |
|16|        │ └─TEMP TABLE ACCESS      |VIEW1(TEMP1)|0       |0           |
|17|        └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET    |item        |1       |16          |
===========================================================================
