|2 |  └─SORT                         |                      |1       |1292        |
|3 |    └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN           |                      |1       |1292        |
|4 |      ├─SUBPLAN SCAN             |dn                    |1       |1288        |
|5 |      │ └─HASH GROUP BY          |                      |1       |1288        |
