|7 |      │     ├─TABLE FULL SCAN    |store                 |12      |3           |
|8 |      │     └─HASH JOIN          |                      |118     |1238        |
|9 |      │       ├─TABLE FULL SCAN  |date_dim              |162     |62          |
|10|      │       └─HASH JOIN        |                      |268     |1116        |
|11|      │         ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|household_demographics|23      |19          |
|12|      │         └─TABLE FULL SCAN|store_sales           |5000    |673         |
|13|      └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET    |customer              |1       |16          |
===================================================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([customer.c_last_name], [customer.c_first_name], [customer.c_salutation], [customer.c_preferred_cust_flag], [dn.ss_ticket_number], [dn.cnt]), filter(nil)
  1 - output([customer.c_last_name], [customer.c_first_name], [customer.c_salutation], [customer.c_preferred_cust_flag], [dn.ss_ticket_number], [dn.cnt]), filter(nil)
